Package: dimsprepr
Title: dimsprepr: An R Package for End-to-End Preprocessing of
    Direct-Injection Metabolomics Data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("John Lennon", "Calorio", , "jllcalorio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for end-to-end preprocessing of direct-injection
    metabolomics data — missing value filtering, imputation, signal drift
    and batch correction, normalization, transformation, scaling, and
    quality filtering — in a single reproducible pipeline.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://jllcalorio.github.io/dimsprepr
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    BiocParallel,
    ggplot2,
    grDevices,
    grid,
    gridExtra,
    imputeLCMD,
    matrixStats,
    mice,
    parallelly,
    pmp,
    stats,
    sva,
    tools,
    vsn
VignetteBuilder: 
    knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
Encoding: UTF-8
